// Breadth First Search

In BFS we use the Queue.
We will first take the starting point and put it in the stack.
We will start deleting from the front and rear(last).
Initially both front and rear will be at the same place.
We will add the element and start deleting the element and we will put the adjacent of the deleted element.
We will repeat the above step and also made one output visited list and we will add put the deleted node.
We will repeat the above process until the stack empty.
and return the visited node / output.
